\details{
\subsection{Thresholds}{

Two thresholds control which suboptimal trees are retained:
\itemize{
\item \verb{$absolute_threshold} — the maximum number of extra steps above the
best tree length.
\item \verb{$relative_threshold} — the maximum proportional excess above the
length of the tree being swapped, as a value between 0 and 1.
}
}

